author: Chip Patterson
title: SEC on CBS Podcast: Week 6 ATS picks and a couple birthdays
text:
It's the birthday edition of the SEC on CBS Podcast , as both Tom Fornelli and Jerry Hinnen celebrated their day of arrival into this world in the last week. My gift to them is 50 minutes of college football previewing and against-the-spread picking, plus whatever I choose off their Amazon wish list. 
We begin in the SEC with Tennessee - Georgia , Alabama - Arkansas and Florida - Missouri before taking it national with Michigan - Northwestern (with Over/Under picks too!), Georgia Tech - Clemson , Miami - Florida State , Utah - Cal and much, much more. 
Don't forget there are many ways to access the SEC on CBS Sports Podcast. You can download to MP3s below or subscribe on iTunes , Stitcher Radio and TuneIn .
